{"title":"蓝色的海疆","authors":["纪鹏"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":11,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝色的海疆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纪鹏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快艇夜击"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海上雾茫茫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"空中云遮月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快艇夜伏击，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚步多轻捷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船外海浪高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船内心如铁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大海是纸，快艇是笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歼敌的誓言浪上写。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海上轻骑隐藏在波涛里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军机的秘密一丝不能泄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪峰浪谷布下杀敌阵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海上雷池一步不准越。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信号枪飞出一颗星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"条条快艇出战列，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜海射出利箭一支支，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"航迹的浪花白如雪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪里来的“不速客”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鱼雷笑着去迎接，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎来的“客人”都是“太平号”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海战史上又翻新一页。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捉海蟹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海潮落，月儿明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三三两两海边行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提着铁桶和网兜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带上手套拿着手电筒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"假日傍晚捉海蟹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耐心、沉着要机警，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石缝，沙滩细搜索，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发现目标，快开“探照灯”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手电照得海蟹发了懵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举起双夹不敢动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁让你贪吃，如今当俘虏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一会儿抓了大半桶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海波摇明月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军港亮起万点星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滩头篝火烧红了海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脸盆煮蟹做佳羹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捉蟹的本领要练好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艺高胆大不留情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在祖国的钢铁海疆上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪准“蟹”横行。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}